{"data":[{"date":"07:26 15/06","title":"5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018: Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a l\u00e0 g\u00ec so v\u1edbi h\u1ecd!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/top-5-ung-vien-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-brazil-duc-chua-la-gi-so-voi-ho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u0103ng k\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o nh\u01b0 Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c hay Ph\u00e1p song h\u1ecd \u1ea9n ch\u1ee9a s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Video 5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6ChFe1-f_e4\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>1. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/dt-thuy-si-tai-world-cup-2018-co-xung-voi-hang-6-the-gioi-421-188125.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</span></strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o gi\u1eefa kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Vladimir Petkovic, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i h\u01a1n v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y khoa h\u1ecdc. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 10 trong s\u1ed1 12 tr\u1eadn, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 1 thua, 1 h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>2. Croatia</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nCroatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u201cch\u00fa ng\u1ef1a \u00f4\u201d c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Nh\u1eefng Ivan Rakitic, Luka Modric, Ivan Perisic hay Mario Mandzukic v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb9p tr\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Video 5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 l\u0103ng k\u00ednh Bongda24hvn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Video 5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 l\u0103ng k\u00ednh Bongda24hvn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Video-5-ung-vien-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-lang-kinh-Bongda24hvn-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>3. Colombia</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2014, Colombia \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi t\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Brazil. N\u0103m nay, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 James Rodriguez hay Radamel Falcao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>4. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/dt-uruguay-tai-world-cup-2018-duong-ta-thang-tien-421-187908.html\" target=\"_blank\">Uruguay</span></strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 th\u1edf v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp, Nga v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Uruguay d\u1ec5 nh\u01b0\u2026 \u0103n b\u00e1nh. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111i s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh lu\u00f4n ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i d\u00e0i \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a l\u00e0 g\u00ec so v\u1edbi h\u1ecd! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a l\u00e0 g\u00ec so v\u1edbi h\u1ecd! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/5-ung-vien-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-Brazil,-Duc-chua-la-gi-so-voi-ho!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T\u00a0Uruguay</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>5. B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Ngo\u00e0i Cris Ronaldo, hi\u1ec7n Seleccao \u0111\u00e3 s\u1ea3n sinh m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb trung s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Euro 2016, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"174","checkdouble":"188520"},{"date":"07:44 15/06","title":"S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 9: Nh\u1eadt k\u00fd ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-9-nhat-ky-world-cup-ngay-khai-mac.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng Bongda24h.vn nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u 14/6 c\u00f2n \u0111ang n\u00f3ng h\u1ed5i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Clip S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 9:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IQP2TuA-Wbw\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf m\u00e0n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. L\u1ec5 khai m\u1ea1c di\u1ec5n ra trong v\u00f2ng 20 ph\u00fat cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n x\u1ee9 b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng qua \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t l\u1ec5 khai m\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t g\u1eedi \u0111i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p to l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Vladimir Putin c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m vui c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi khi Nga l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau l\u1ec5 khai m\u1ea1c r\u1ed9n r\u00e0ng, Nga v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n Luzhniki (Moskva) v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 nh\u00e0, \u201cG\u1ea5u Nga\u201d d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c1 5 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 n\u1ed9i dung \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i t\u1edbi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 th\u00f4ng qua clip d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean truy c\u1eadp Bongda24h.vn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00e9!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean <span href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZAiun8-d60VU6Px95pbGPA/videos\" target=\"_blank\">k\u00eanh Youtube c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-5-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p2-421-188290.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-5-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-5-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p2-421-188290.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 5: \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (P2)</span><br>\r\n<span>S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 \u0111i qua 3 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n t\u1eebng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-3-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p1-421-188173.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/10/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-3-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-3-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p1-421-188173.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 3: \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (P1)</span><br>\r\n<span>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u00e2u, Bongda24h.vn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi clip S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 3. H\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng nhau b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111i\u1ec3m...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBongda24h.vn (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"173","checkdouble":"188521"},{"date":"07:53 15/06","title":"L\u1ec5 khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 s\u1eafc m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/le-khai-mac-world-cup-2018-ruc-ro-sac-mau-cua-chu-nha-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kieran Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Harry Kane r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Kane l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao. 3 m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u1ec1u ghi tr\u00ean 20 b\u00e0n \u1edf Premier League. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua anh c\u00f3 30 b\u00e0n, k\u00e9m Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Salah 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane muon DT Anh len ngoi vo dich\" title=\"Kane mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Kane-se-la-Vua-pha-luoi-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kane l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao c\u00f9ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 vinh d\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Harry Kane, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-world-cup-421-188300.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kane n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh \u0111i s\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKieran Trippier, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Harry Kane \u1edf Tottenham \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Harry Kane, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u1ecdi t\u01b0 th\u1ebf. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf c\u1ea3 CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Kane \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup 2018&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kieran Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Harry Kane r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane doi truong tuyen Anh\" title=\"Kane doi truong tuyen Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/kieran-trippier-anh-khong-chi-co-minh-harry-kane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kieran Trippier cho r\u1eb1ng Kane quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Raheem Sterling hay Dele Alli ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o c\u1ea3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh&nbsp;b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i g\u1eafn k\u1ebft&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf World Cup 2014 t\u1ea1i Brazil, song Trippier kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t, Anh t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"172","checkdouble":"188522"},{"date":"07:53 15/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 15/6: 4 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u0110N th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn m\u1edf m\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/tin-nong-world-cup-2018-ngay-156-4-tuyen-thu-bdn-that-nghiep-truoc-dai-chien-mo-man.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (15/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha r\u1ed1i ren tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 24h t\u1edbi, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ngay trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. Trong khi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o scandal thay t\u01b0\u1edbng 48 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi khai m\u1ea1c World Cup r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ramos \u1ea9u \u0111\u1ea3 v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u00ec ph\u00eda B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e2m l\u00fd tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 4 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \"Seleccao\" t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u1eeba l\u00e2m v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \"th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p\". C\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 William Carvalho, Bruno Fernandes, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gelson Martins v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Rui Patricio v\u1eeba ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB Sporting v\u00ec m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Fernando Santos \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00eam nay.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/3_2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u00f4m m\u1ed9ng l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 Brazil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho Brazil. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 1h s\u00e1ng 18/6. Shaqiri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u201cMessi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\u201d cho r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe 100% s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1ea5u Australia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, Kylian Mbappe d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 19 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Australia ng\u00e0y 16/6 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-sau-chan-thuong-gap-phai-421-188352.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/mbappe-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-sau-chan-thuong-gap-phai.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-sau-chan-thuong-gap-phai-421-188352.html\">Mbappe ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i</span><br>\r\n<span>Kylian Mbappe ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn NHM \u0110T Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng, ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Kane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kieran Trippier kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Trippier v\u00e0 Kane l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Tottenham. Theo Trippier, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u01b0 Alli, Sterling hay Vardy c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"171","checkdouble":"188523"},{"date":"08:00 15/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay (19h ng\u00e0y 15/6): Salah c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng\u2026","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-19h-ngay-156-salah-co-hay-khong-khong-quan-trong.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00f4ng qua ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Cuper, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng Salah v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay t\u1ed1i nay (15/6). Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Salah c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y, Mohamed Salah l\u1ea1c quan t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t ngay tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u1edbi Uruguay. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng vai \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 sau 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Salah g\u1ee3i cho C\u0110V \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1eafc Phi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u1ea5t an.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt may, Salah v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. \u1ede nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang ng\u00e0y 15/6 h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t, tham gia c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. V\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ai-cap-nhan-tin-vui-bat-ngo-tu-thanh-salah-421-188498.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ai C\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn tin vui b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb &ldquo;Th\u00e1nh Salah&rdquo;</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay 19h ng\u00e0y 156 Salah kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay 19h ng\u00e0y 156 Salah kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Nhan-dinh-Ai-Cap-vs-Uruguay-19h-ngay-156-Salah-khong-quan-trong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Salah nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Hector Cuper th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o, Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 100% s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ef1c vui \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n bi\u1ebfn l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAi C\u1eadp s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Mo Salah. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh &ldquo;C\u00e1c Pharaoh&rdquo;. C\u00f3 anh, s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y, tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Liverpool nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t h\u1ed3n khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 anh \u1edf 2/3 cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp v\u1eabn l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n. \u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u00e0 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1990 t\u1edbi nay. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Cuper r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu Salah ra s\u00e2n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 r\u1ee7i ro l\u1edbn, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 che gi\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Ai Cap vs Uruguay\" title=\"Preview Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Ai-Cap-vs-Uruguay.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay c\u00f3 ch\u00fat thay \u0111\u1ed5i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Salah ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng. Anh v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ednh \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i. Trong b\u1ea3ng A, Uruguay l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/nga-huy-diet-saudi-arabia-salah-va-luis-suarez-buoc-phai-mot-mat-mot-con-466-188511.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nga, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Saudi Arabia 5-0</span> ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2, Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Nga trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn n\u00f3i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec &ldquo;6 \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo;. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i \u1edf s\u00e2n Saint-Petersburg n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0 c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Uruguay kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khu v\u1ef1c Nam M\u1ef9, h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Argentina, Colombia r\u1ed3i Chile&hellip; \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 may m\u1eafn khi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a La Celeste v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i. N\u1ebfu Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Salah, Uruguay c\u00f3 nguy\u00ean b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Edinson Cavani \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Uruguay xep thu 2 vong loai\" title=\"Uruguay xep thu 2 vong loai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/DT-Uruguay-tai-World-Cup-2018-Duong-ta-thang-tien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 g\u00ec, Uruguay v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng Rodrigo Bentancur, Matias Vecino \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 r\u1ed3i Jose Maria Gimenez, Diego Godin \u1edf h\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. \u1ede c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn, Uruguay \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i tr\u1ea3i d\u00e0i v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp. \u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOscar Tabarez l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a Uruguay t\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 World Cup n\u0103m 2010 v\u00e0 v\u00f2ng 1/8 n\u0103m 2014. \u00d4ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. V\u1edbi ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Uruguay ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nga th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 t\u1eeb m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp. Uruguay c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. C\u00f3 Salah hay kh\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc Phi v\u1eabn \u1edf &ldquo;chi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1edbi&rdquo; so v\u1edbi Uruguay v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cho h\u1ecd trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nAi C\u1eadp (4-2-3-1):</strong> 1.Hadary &ndash; 7.Fathy, 6.Hegazi, 2.Gabr, 13.Shafy &ndash; 17.Elneny, 8.Hamed &ndash; 10.Salah, 19.Said, 21.Trezeguet &ndash; 9.Mohsen.<br>\r\n<strong>Uruguay (4-3-1-2):</strong> 1.Muslera &ndash; 16.Pereira, 2.Gimenez, 3.Godin, 22.Caceres &ndash; 6.Bentancur, 15.Vecino, 8.Nandez &ndash; 10.Arrascaeta &ndash; 9.Suarez, 21.Cavani.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Uruguay th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Maroc vs Iran\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Mar\u1ed1c vs Iran\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Maroc-vs-Iran-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"170","checkdouble":"188524"},{"date":"08:38 15/06","title":"Kieran Trippier: \"Anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u00ecnh Harry Kane\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/kieran-trippier-anh-khong-chi-co-minh-harry-kane.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kieran Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Harry Kane r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Kane l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao. 3 m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u1ec1u ghi tr\u00ean 20 b\u00e0n \u1edf Premier League. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua anh c\u00f3 30 b\u00e0n, k\u00e9m Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Salah 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane muon DT Anh len ngoi vo dich\" title=\"Kane mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Kane-se-la-Vua-pha-luoi-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kane l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao c\u00f9ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 vinh d\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Harry Kane, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-world-cup-421-188300.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kane n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh \u0111i s\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKieran Trippier, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Harry Kane \u1edf Tottenham \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Harry Kane, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u1ecdi t\u01b0 th\u1ebf. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf c\u1ea3 CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Kane \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup 2018&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kieran Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Harry Kane r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane doi truong tuyen Anh\" title=\"Kane doi truong tuyen Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/kieran-trippier-anh-khong-chi-co-minh-harry-kane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kieran Trippier cho r\u1eb1ng Kane quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Raheem Sterling hay Dele Alli ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o c\u1ea3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh&nbsp;b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i g\u1eafn k\u1ebft&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf World Cup 2014 t\u1ea1i Brazil, song Trippier kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t, Anh t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"169","checkdouble":"188525"},{"date":"08:54 15/06","title":"Diego Godin: \"Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 Salah hay kh\u00f4ng c\u0169ng v\u1eady th\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/diego-godin-ai-cap-co-salah-hay-khong-cung-vay-thoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Diego Godin ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah hay kh\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Godin kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Salah c\u00f3 ra s\u00e2n hay kh\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Ai C\u1eadp, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Godin phat bieu ve Salah\" title=\"Godin ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/diego-godin-ai-cap-co-salah-hay-khong-cung-vay-thoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Godin ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1ea3ng A c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin bu\u1ed3n v\u1edbi Uruguay, b\u1edfi Salah l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Diego Godin ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah hay kh\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Uruguay s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00ec m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Salah l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Uruguay s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u kh\u00e1 k\u1ef9 l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Salah, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n hay kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Godin cho r\u1eb1ng Ramos v\u00f4 t\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergio Ramos ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m khi\u1ebfn Salah d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, Godin nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mohamed Salah chan thuong sau pha va cham voi Sergio Ramos.\" title=\"Mohamed Salah ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Sergio Ramos.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/28/salah-phat-bieu-ve-chan-thuong-o-chung-ket-c1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Godin cho r\u1eb1ng Ramos kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00e1c \u00fd khi\u1ebfn Salah ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Ramos kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng va ch\u1ea1m b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng may \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Salah. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 xem l\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1ea3y ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin Ramos kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00e1c \u00fd&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp, Uruguay s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea2 R\u1eadp X\u00ea \u00dat v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"168","checkdouble":"188526"},{"date":"08:12 15/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha (1h ng\u00e0y 16/6): Khi \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i\u2026","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-166-khi-bo-tot-lac-loi.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ec9 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y gh\u00ea g\u1edbm v\u00e0 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Lopetegui b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 4 v\u1eeba qua, Real Madrid c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 Julen Lopetegui l\u00e0 HLV m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2018/19. Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 ng\u00e0y sau, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nguyen-nhan-thuc-su-dang-sau-viec-hlv-lopetegui-bi-tbn-sa-thai-421-188413.html\" target=\"_blank\">nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb1ng sau vi\u1ec7c HLV Lopetegui b\u1ecb TBN sa th\u1ea3i</span>. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 40 tu\u1ed5i, m\u1edbi l\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 (RFEF) kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u cho hay h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. Rubiales v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft tin Lopetegui \u0111\u1ebfn Real v\u00e0i gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1h ng\u00e0y 166 B\u00f2 t\u00f3t l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1h ng\u00e0y 166 B\u00f2 t\u00f3t l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Nhan-dinh-Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Tay-Ban-Nha-1h-ngay-166-Bo-tot-lac-loi-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Lopetegui r\u1eddi TBN m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ebd b\u00e0ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLi\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh x\u1eed v\u00f4 ph\u00e9p t\u1eafc. H\u1ecd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean ti\u1ec1n l\u1ec7 x\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y kh\u00f4n l\u01b0\u1eddng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup, ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0110TQG n\u00e0o sa th\u1ea3i HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1ec9 1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra qu\u00e2n. Kh\u00f4ng ai mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 20 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2016 t\u1edbi nay, Lopetegui \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i (th\u1eafng 14, h\u00f2a 6). Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00edch, c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap La Roja h\u1ed3i sinh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i. 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn l\u00e0 World Cup 2014 v\u00e0 Euro 2016 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Vicente Del Bosque, TBN \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN vs Thuy Si doi hinh\" title=\"TBN vs Thuy Si doi hinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/DT-Tay-Ban-Nha-Dan-bo-tot-dang-bi-ton-thuong-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">La Roja \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng r\u1ed3i v\u00f2ng 1/8 d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 dung h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7. M\u1ed9t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u binh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap &ldquo;B\u00f2 t\u00f3t&rdquo; l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Sergio Ramos, Gerard Pique, Andres Iniesta hay David Silva&hellip; <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1t khao th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i \u0110TQG nh\u01b0 Dani Carvajal, Koke, Thiago Alcantara, Isco hay Marco Asensio&hellip; T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u h\u00f2a v\u00e0o l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha bay cao v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Italia (v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018) hay 6-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina (Giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tbn-dai-loan-ramos-tan-nhau-voi-chu-tich-ngay-tren-san-tap-421-188503.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/tbn-dai-loan-ramos-tan-nhau-voi-chu-tich-ngay-tren-san-tap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tbn-dai-loan-ramos-tan-nhau-voi-chu-tich-ngay-tren-san-tap-421-188503.html\">TBN \u0111\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1n: Ramos &ldquo;t\u1ea9n&rdquo; nhau v\u1edbi Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp</span><br>\r\n<span>Nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 scandal c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, khi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Sergio Ramos \u1ea9u \u0111\u1ea3 v\u1edbi Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng thi\u1ebfu \u0111i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/lopetegui-bat-khoc-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-188509.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lopetegui - ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Real</span>, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea1ch ra 2 n\u0103m qua c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00f4i theo s\u00f4ng, theo bi\u1ec3n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh &ldquo;B\u00f2 t\u00f3t&rdquo; gi\u1edd \u0111ang l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i d\u01b0\u1edbi tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi Fernando Hierro. Ch\u1ec9 2 ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u00edt \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ef1u Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a RFEF \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0i to\u00e1n t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p v\u1edbi Hierro. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1edbi World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 do Lopetegui ch\u1ecdn ra v\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd. Kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 10/23 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a TBN hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 theo \u00f4ng chinh chi\u1ebfn trong c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb U19 t\u1edbi U21 qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Bo Dao Nha vs Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"Preview B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1562018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd b\u1ecb t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00ec Lopetegui</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang v\u00e0o l\u00fac \u0111ang kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3, m\u1ed9t T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi thay HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p ngay ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. So v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m khi \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i Euro 2016, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Seleccao c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 Cristiano Ronaldo, Rui Patr\u00edcio, Pepe, Joao Moutinho, Ricardo Quaresma&hellip; song \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i tr\u1ebb trung, gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u1eefng m\u1ea1nh gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 th\u1eafng 9 trong s\u1ed1 10 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1edbi VCK World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BDN ngoi sao Ronaldo\" title=\"BDN ngoi sao Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/Nhan-dinh-Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Algeria-(02h15-ngay-86)-Ha-guc-Bay-Cao-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u0110N&nbsp;c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh. Ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, nh\u1eefng Andre Silva, Goncalo Guedes, Gelson Martins, Bernardo Silva&hellip; s\u1ebd h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi CR7 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o b\u00e3 tr\u1ea7u tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 Lopetegui ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng \u00edt th\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u. Qua \u0111\u00f3, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n song xem ra s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Olimpiyskiy (Sochi).<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nB\u0110N (4-4-2):</strong> 1.Patr\u00edcio - 21.C\u00e9dric, 3.Pepe, 6.Fonte, 5.Guerreiro - 11.Bernardo Silva, 14.Carvalho, 10.M\u00e1rio, 20.Quaresma - 7.Ronaldo, 9.Andre Silva<br>\r\n<strong>TBN (4-3-3): </strong>1.De Gea - 12.Odriozola, 3.Piqu\u00e9, 15.Ramos, 18.Alba - 10.Thiago, 5.Busquets, 6.Iniesta - 22.Isco, 19.Costa - 21.David Silva.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: H\u00f2a 1-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Bo Dao Nha vs Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/BDN-vs-TBN-(4-4-2-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"167","checkdouble":"188527"},{"date":"08:20 15/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran (22h00 ng\u00e0y 15/6): Tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn sinh t\u1eed","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhan-dinh-ma-roc-vs-iran-22h00-ngay-156-tran-chien-sinh-tu.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng mong manh trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ma R\u1ed1c l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMa R\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. H\u1ecd d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C, x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0. Sau 5 tr\u1eadn, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Renard b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran (22h00 ng\u00e0y 156) Tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn sinh t\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran (22h00 ng\u00e0y 156) Tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn sinh t\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Nhan-dinh-Ma-Roc-vs-Iran-(22h00-ngay-156)-Tran-chien-sinh-tu-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ma R\u1ed1c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMedhi Benatia v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n n\u00e0o. V\u1edbi 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 5 tr\u1eadn, Ma R\u1ed1c gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng C, h\u01a1n B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. H\u1ecd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i World Cup sau 20 n\u0103m v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Renard \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t Ma R\u1ed1c v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. H\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u Phi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn duy nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-maroc-tai-world-cup-2018-20-nam-sau-moi-chuyen-co-khac-421-188069.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/8/dt-maroc-tai-world-cup-2018-20-nam-sau-moi-chuyen-co-khac.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-maroc-tai-world-cup-2018-20-nam-sau-moi-chuyen-co-khac-421-188069.html\">\u0110T Ma-r\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: 20 n\u0103m sau, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 kh\u00e1c?</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Ma-r\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n. Li\u1ec7u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u sau 20 n\u0103m, &ldquo;S\u01b0 t\u1eed d\u00e3y Atlas&rdquo; c\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho World Cup 2018, Ma R\u1ed1c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Estonia 3-1, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 n\u1eefa l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Slovakia.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 5 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho World Cup 2018, Ma R\u1ed1c b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 1 l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Herve Renard \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao khi b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 8/2017 \u0111\u1ebfn nay.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede VCK World Cup 2018, Ma R\u1ed1c r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Iran. So v\u1edbi 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia, Ma R\u1ed1c b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Herve Renard s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN v\u00e0 B\u0110N.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Maroc vs Iran\" title=\"Preview Mar\u1ed1c vs Iran\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Ma-Roc-vs-Iran.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Mar\u1ed1c vs Iran trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTr\u1eadn Ma R\u1ed1c vs Iran, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1edbi gi\u00fap h\u1ecd nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng mong manh trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Ma R\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. N\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Medhi Benatia, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i cho Bayern v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Achraf Hakimi \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid, m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Amine Harit \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Schalke hay Hakim-Ziyech, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Ajax.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, Ma R\u1ed1c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Iran b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng B</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Ma R\u1ed1c, Iran c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i. Theo \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c1, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. K\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i, Iran th\u1eafng 6, h\u00f2a 4, b\u1ecf t\u00fai t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 22 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Iran bi danh gia thap nhat bang B\" title=\"Iran b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng B\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/iran.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Iran b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng B</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIran c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Algeria v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Nga v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u0169ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Iran g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 4 l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Trong s\u1ed1 12 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1, thua 8 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 3.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIran hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p. B\u1edfi v\u1eady \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn sinh t\u1eed v\u1edbi Ma R\u1ed1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Iran kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t cho World Cup 2018. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Ma R\u1ed1c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Maroc vs Iran\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Mar\u1ed1c vs Iran\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Maroc-vs-Iran-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Mar\u1ed1c vs Iran</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 2-1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"166","checkdouble":"188528"},{"date":"08:51 15/06","title":"Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/ramos-phat-bieu-soc-truoc-tran-tay-ban-nha-vs-bo-dao-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Sergio Ramos \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c.</h2><h2>\"Cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o n\u00e0y\u00a0nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1m ma v\u1eady\"</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn khai m\u00e0n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-0 c\u1ee7a \u0110T ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i qua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia, v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 15/6, NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao gi\u1eefa hai n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sergio Ramos \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u khi anh l\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/ramos-phat-bieu-soc-truoc-tran-tay-ban-nha-vs-bo-dao-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu.\u00a0Julen Lopetegui\u00a0l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn Nga v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018\u201d, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Real cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui, Ramos nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m (sa th\u1ea3i Lopetegui) v\u00e0 n\u00f3 l\u00e0m cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed3n nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i g\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o l\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t. \u0110TQG quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n thua. T\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai nghi ng\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra CV c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Ramos c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 TBN kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau khi <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nong-dt-tay-ban-nha-sa-thai-hlv-lopetegui-truoc-thoi-han-421-188412.html\" target=\"_blank\">L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd sa th\u1ea3i HLV Lopetegui</span>. \u201cB\u00ean trong trung t\u00e2m hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u (r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai) v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n s\u1edbm qu\u00ean \u0111i s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u00f4i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng (\u1edf World Cup), \u201cmang theo\u201d hi v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. S\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t tham v\u1ecdng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai ng\u00e0y\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau h\u01a1n n\u1eeda gi\u1edd \u201c\u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ed\u201d v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi h\u00f3c b\u00faa v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Ramos t\u1ecf ra m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \"T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ra kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e2y, bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e1m tang v\u1eady. Ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-166-khi-bo-tot-lac-loi-421-188527.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span> s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1 gi\u1edd r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai (16/6) gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/euro-2012--nhip-song-euro/tay-ban-nha-vs-bo-dao-nha-moi-han-ben-ban-dao-iberia-298-50282.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2012/6/bodaonhatungkhientaybannhaomhantaieuro2004-2012626113414.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/euro-2012--nhip-song-euro/tay-ban-nha-vs-bo-dao-nha-moi-han-ben-ban-dao-iberia-298-50282.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: M\u1ed1i h\u1eadn b\u00ean b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia</span><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea9y T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha gi\u00e1p chi\u1ebfn \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sinh t\u1eed nh\u1eb1m gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i chung k\u1ebft Euro 2012. M\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"165","checkdouble":"188529"},{"date":"04:16 15/06","title":"HLV \u0110T Saudi Arabia x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 sau khi thua th\u1ea3m Nga \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/hlv-dt-saudi-arabia-xau-ho-sau-khi-thua-tham-nga-o-tran-mo-man.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Juan Antonio Pizzi c\u1ee7a Saudi Arabia th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng th\u1ea5y x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua th\u1ea3m 0-5 khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga ngay trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Saudi Arabia thua th\u1ea3m<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong BXH FIFA (67 sao v\u1edbi 70), Saudi Arabia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd thua \u0111\u1eadm 0-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u1ecf nhoi b\u1edfi hai tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Uruguay.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV DT Saudi Arabia xau ho vi tran thua tham Nga.\" title=\"HLV \u0110T Saudi Arabia x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 v\u00ec tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m Nga.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/hlv-dt-saudi-arabia-xau-ho-sau-khi-thua-tham-nga-o-tran-mo-man.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV \u0110T Saudi Arabia x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 v\u00ec tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m Nga.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, HLV Juan Antonio Pizzi b\u00e0y t\u1ecf: &quot;\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i qu\u00ean \u0111i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t n\u0103m qua, Juan Antonio Pizzi l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia th\u1ee9 ba ng\u1ed3i l\u00ean chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Saudi Arabia, sau nh\u1eefng Bert van Marwijk v\u00e0 Edgardo Bauza. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u1ecb HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd s\u1edbm n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m ra \u0111i sau khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Juan Antonio Pizzi v\u1eabn l\u1ea1c quan cho r\u1eb1ng Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo: &quot;D\u00f9 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd tri\u1ec3n khai l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. T\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i, tin v\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng tri\u1ec3n khai l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra. D\u00f9 sao v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 Uruguay \u1edf tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 22h00 ng\u00e0y 20/6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/nga-vs-saudi-arabia-khai-mac-world-cup-2018-463-188481.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/ket-qua-nga-vs-saudi-arabia-tran-dau-bang-a-world-cup-2018.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/nga-vs-saudi-arabia-khai-mac-world-cup-2018-463-188481.html\">Nga 5-0 Saudi Arabia (KT): Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 World Cup 2018 ra qu\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng h\u01a1n</span><br />\r\nD\u00f9 l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng Nga kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5 sao qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed7i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"164","checkdouble":"188506"},{"date":"04:34 15/06","title":"HLV Stanislav Cherchesov: \"\u0110T Nga ph\u1ea3i qu\u00ean ngay chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/hlv-stanislav-cherchesov-dt-nga-phai-quen-ngay-chien-thang-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Stanislav Cherchesov c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nga bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1m d\u1eebng cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 nghe \u0111i\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Vladimir Putin sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \"5 sao\".</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1m ho\u00e3n \u0111\u1ec3 nghe \u0111i\u1ec7n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 5-0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadp n\u00ean h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, HLV Stanislav Cherchesov c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nga \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi ch\u00fac m\u1eebng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1m ng\u01b0ng cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 nghe \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eeb T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Nga Vladimir Putin.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Stanislav Cherchesov \u0110T Nga ph\u1ea3i qu\u00ean ngay chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Stanislav Cherchesov \u0110T Nga ph\u1ea3i qu\u00ean ngay chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Stanislav-Cherchesov.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Stanislav Cherchesov cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Nga kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Li\u00ean bang \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi ch\u00fac m\u1eebng&quot; - HLV Cherchesov h\u00f3m h\u1ec9nh n\u00f3i: &quot;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u00f4i g\u1eedi l\u1eddi ch\u00fac m\u1eebng t\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi \u0110T Nga khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i trong hai tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo g\u1eb7p Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Uruguay. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0110T Nga s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Cherchesov r\u00e8n gi\u0169a ngay trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Saudi Arabia khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 th\u1eafng to \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng HLV Cherchesov kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan khi hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, \u0110T Nga c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alan Dzagoev d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, HLV Cherchesov kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Nga c\u1ea7n qu\u00ean ngay chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u01b0ng hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n. OK. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 5-0 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ba \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Confederations Cup h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn, gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac sang trang v\u00e0 qu\u00ean ngay tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba qua \u0111i&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Nga s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Ai C\u1eadp \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 20/6.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/alan-dzagoev-chan-thuong-co-nguy-co-mat-world-cup-2018-465-188505.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/alan-dzagoev-chan-thuong-co-nguy-co-mat-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/alan-dzagoev-chan-thuong-co-nguy-co-mat-world-cup-2018-465-188505.html\">Alan Dzagoev ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</span><br />\r\nAlan Dzagoev ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t kho\u1ea3ng 2 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay s\u1edbm v\u1edbi World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"163","checkdouble":"188507"},{"date":"05:19 15/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Denis Cheryshev c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5 sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/denis-cheryshev-can-loi-sau-chien-thang-5-sao-cua-dt-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Saudi Arabia v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 5-0 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng A tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01a1n, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Nga c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u01b0u th\u1ebf<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay t\u1eeb khi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ph\u00e2n b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng Nga \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 can thi\u1ec7p v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3. B\u1ea3ng A n\u01a1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nga \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 to\u00e0n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. \u0110T Uruguay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, trong khi Saudi Arabia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u1ea5p th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 (ch\u1ec9 tr\u00ean Nga).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Saudi Arabia Salah v\u00e0 Luis Suarez m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Saudi Arabia Salah v\u00e0 Luis Suarez m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/nga-huy-diet-saudi-arabia-salah-va-luis-suarez-buoc-phai-mot-mat-mot-con.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Saudi Arabia \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eafm l\u1ea5y th\u1ebf ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed ngay c\u1ea3 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0110T Nga c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 khi \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f3. H\u1ecd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Saudi Arabia, Ai C\u1eadp r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn Uruguay \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 5-0 gi\u00fap \u0110T Nga c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u1edbi ba \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 +5, \u0110T Nga ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu h\u00f2a trong c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn cho HLV Stanislav Cherchesov d\u1ec5 toan t\u00ednh h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nga c\u0169ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ea9y Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Uruguay v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3. \u0110T Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00edu gi\u1eef hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, th\u1ebf n\u00ean hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Nga s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuc dien bang A tro nen kho luong sau khi DT Nga huy diet Saudi Arabia.\" title=\"C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng A tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng sau khi \u0110T Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Saudi Arabia.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/bang-a.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng A tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng sau khi \u0110T Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Saudi Arabia.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o thua trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Uruguay s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn, th\u1ebf n\u00ean Nga ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 &quot;t\u1ecda s\u01a1n xem h\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ea5u&quot;. Nh\u00ecn chung, vi\u1ec7c th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Saudi Arabia gi\u00fap Nga c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh th\u1ebf ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock out c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea9y Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Uruguay v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ec5 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia, \u0110T Nga sau khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u1ea7n lui v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. HLV Cherchesov d\u00f9ng ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e8n gi\u0169a c\u00e1c b\u00e0i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng cho \u0110T Nga, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng khi g\u1eb7p hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean c\u01a1 l\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Uruguay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Viec Nga huy diet Saudi Arabia khien Ai Cap va Uruguay roi vao the kho.\" title=\"Vi\u1ec7c Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Saudi Arabia khi\u1ebfn Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Uruguay r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/ai-cap-vs-uruguay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Vi\u1ec7c Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Saudi Arabia khi\u1ebfn Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Uruguay r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u00ean, \u0110T Nga ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a l\u00e0 n\u1eafm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Nga kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng trong c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn, trong khi m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Nga trong th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng. Gi\u1eefa m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Nga c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1ec3 toan t\u00ednh h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Nga ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng, s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i. HLV Cherchesov c\u0169ng x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n cho \u0110T Nga t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 kh\u1edfi tranh. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhu\u1ea7n nhuy\u1ec5n trong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng, Nga c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Ai C\u1eadp ho\u1eb7c Uruguay \u00f4m tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn. Denis Cheryshev l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn nguy hi\u1ec3m khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eb1ng k\u00e8o tr\u00e1i c\u1ef1c kh\u00e9o. Aleksandr Golovin c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m khi c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loi the san nha cung loi choi phong ngu phan cong khien Nga tro thanh doi thu cuc ky kho chiu.\" title=\"L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Nga tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/nga-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Nga tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn hay t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nga trong th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n th\u0103ng hoa khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Nga tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Saudi Arabia c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nga khi\u1ebfn c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Uruguay gi\u1edd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock out.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/nga-vs-saudi-arabia-khai-mac-world-cup-2018-463-188481.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/ket-qua-nga-vs-saudi-arabia-tran-dau-bang-a-world-cup-2018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/nga-vs-saudi-arabia-khai-mac-world-cup-2018-463-188481.html\">Nga 5-0 Saudi Arabia (KT): Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 World Cup 2018 ra qu\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng h\u01a1n</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng Nga kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5 sao qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed7i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"162","checkdouble":"188508"},{"date":"05:28 15/06","title":"Lopetegui b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/lopetegui-bat-khoc-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00fang v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Nga vs Saudi Arabia, th\u00ec t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Real Madrid t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o quan tr\u1ecdng ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Julen Lopetegui.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">M\u1edf m\u00e0n bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez n\u00f3i: \"Th\u1ef1c ra, Cch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y sau khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> k\u1ebft th\u00fac, khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh quang. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp x\u1ea3y ra m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y qua, th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1edf ra trang m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \"Madridista\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Real k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra v\u1edbi Lopetegui t\u1ea1i Madrid.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft Real v\u00e0 n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft Real v\u00e0 n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Real-Madrid-present-new-coach-Julen-Lopetegui.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u00f9ng t\u00e2n hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Lopetegui. \u1ea2nh: Reuters.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, Lopetegui cho bi\u1ebft t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n HLV t\u1ea1i Bernabeu: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trong kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Real kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft n\u00f3i: \u201cSau khi m\u1eb9 t\u00f4i qua \u0111\u1eddi, vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadn tin b\u1ecb \u0110TQG sa th\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n nh\u1ea5t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00f4m nay l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac nh\u1ea5t\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi b\u1ecb h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do sa th\u1ea3i li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan g\u00ec t\u1edbi l\u00fd do chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n hay kh\u00f4ng, Lopetegui t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00e0 cho hay kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. Tuy nhi\u00ean, hi\u1ec7n \u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Rubiales (ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN) h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ki\u1ec3u kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n trung th\u1ef1c v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi khi th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn (gia nh\u1eadp Real) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng khai v\u00e0 che gi\u1ea5u n\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 trung th\u1ef1c h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\", Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \"Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7. Do \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch cho r\u1eb1ng Real \u0111\u00e3 \"\u0103n tr\u1ed9m\" Lopetegui v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00f4 l\u00ed. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"161","checkdouble":"188509"},{"date":"06:04 15/06","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n CLB c\u1ee7a Griezmann m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/17/griezmann-da-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u00e2m ran</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi trong nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng qua. T\u1eeb l\u00fac b\u00e1o ch\u00ed khui ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00f3, Barcelona l\u00e0 s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Griezmann v\u00e0 s\u1ebd mang anh v\u1ec1 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2018 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 Barca t\u1eebng mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng qua video h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng qua video h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/Griezmann-da-cong-bo-tuong-lai-cua-minh-thong-qua-video-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League v\u1edbi Atletico, Griezmann b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u suy t\u00ednh l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u tham v\u1ecdng chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n HLV Diego Simeone c\u00f9ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. N\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cho t\u1edbi c\u00e1ch th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh. Trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n, Griezmann b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i hay \u1edf nh\u01b0 phim bom t\u1ea5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann va video\" title=\"Griezmann va video\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Griezmann-va-video.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M\u1ed9t c\u1ea3nh trong video c\u1ee7a Griezmann</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Griezmann kho\u00e1c t\u1ea5m \u00e1o \u0111en c\u00f3 m\u0169 tr\u00f9m \u0111\u1ee9ng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng le l\u00f3i b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng \u00e1nh \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea7m t\u01b0 nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e2u xa l\u1ea1, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Wanda Metropolitano c\u1ee7a Atletico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d, Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 v\u1eady tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. H\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef cho Atletico ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, hy v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 n\u0103m 2019. H\u1ecd \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Antoine Griezmann tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-la-dai-ca-o-tuyen-phap-421-188449.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/griezmann-la-dai-ca-o-tuyen-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-la-dai-ca-o-tuyen-phap-421-188449.html\">Griezmann l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i ca \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra \u00edt ng\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh - sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-griezmann-se-giup-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-188443.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/mbappe-griezmann-se-giup-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-griezmann-se-giup-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-188443.html\">Mbappe: Griezmann s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\n<span>Kylian Mbappe ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antoine Griezmann, ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i tin r\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico Madrid s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"160","checkdouble":"188510"}]}